message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.DB, cs.LG. The paper deals with conversational question answering over knowledge graphs, which involves natural language processing, machine learning, and information retrieval. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves graph exploration algorithms and database management, which could fall under cs.DB (Databases) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper deals with information retrieval, which could also fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
